    body: `Partners with central banks and ministries of finance to build the monitoring systems regulators use to track financial innovation, liquidity, and systemic risk. Coordinates the G20 Data Gaps Initiative across 24 economies and major multilateral institutions on data for CBDCs, stablecoins, and cryptoassets. Technical lead on the IMF's Monetary and Financial Statistics Advisory Committee, the body that sets global data standards for the financial sector. Product owner of International Financial Statistics, the IMF's flagship global financial data product; designs and delivers training programs for senior policymakers globally.`,
  },
  {
    org: 'World Bank',
    dates: 'June 2016 – May 2018',
