  },
  {
    org: 'Government of India',
    dates: 'March 2015 – September 2015',
    body: `External consultant to the Indian Institute of Corporate Affairs. Developed curriculum and course materials for a self-paced competition economics program — part of the capacity-building effort supporting India's newly established antitrust regime.`,
  },
  {
    org: 'AZB & Partners',
    dates: 'June 2011 – September 2014',
    body: `Led economic analysis across merger control reviews, cartel investigations, and complex antitrust matters before the Competition Commission of India — translating quantitative evidence into submissions in precedent-setting cases, including India's first Google investigation, a defining moment for digital markets regulation in the country.`,
  },
  {
    org: 'Economic Laws Practice',
